fields.description: Baby Bodysuits are a bundle of joy! Made from soft and snuggly 100% cotton, each bodysuit is completely open on one side, making the garment easy to hoop. After adding your embroidered design, sew up the side with a simple straight stitch! Three snaps provide handy access for diaper changes, and the romper is trimmed at the neck, sleeve, and legs with a solid white binding. Baby Bodysuits come in 3-6-month, 6-9 month, and 9-12-month sizes. Whether you’re looking for the perfect baby gift or simply to snuggle in style.
